The song 'Teri Bhabhi' features the lyrics written by Danish Sabri and sung by Javed - Mohsin.
Dev Negi has composed the music for 'Teri Bhabhi'.
The song 'Teri Bhabhi' features Neha Kakkar singing alongside Javed - Mohsin for its chorus.
Sameer Anjaan has written the lyrics for 'Husnn Hai Suhaana New'.
Tanishk Bagchi has recreated the music for 'Husnn Hai Suhaana New', which was originally composed by Anand-Milind.
Chandana Dixit is one of the singers for 'Husnn Hai Suhaana New'. Alongside her, Abhijeet Bhattacharya has also lent his voice to this song.
Shabbir Ahmed is the lyricist for 'Mummy Kassam'.
Tanishk Bagchi has composed and produced the music for 'Mummy Kassam'. Additionally, he also sings this song alongside Ikka.
Udit Narayan is one of the singers for 'Mummy Kassam'. The other singer for this song is Ikka.
Sameer Anjaan has written the lyrics for 'Mirchi Lagi Toh New'.
'Mirchi Lagi Toh New' is remixed by DJ Chetas, but the original music for this song was composed by Anand-Milind.
Rashmi Virag is responsible for writing the lyrics for 'Tere Siva'.
Tanishk Bagchi has also composed and produced the music for 'Tere Siva'. Both Renessa Das and Ash King have lent their voices to this song.
'Coolie No. 1' is the title track for this movie, and Farhad Samji has directed it.
The music for 'Coolie No. 1' is composed by Salim-Sulaiman.
Raj Pandit sings the title track for 'Coolie No. 1'.
